OL,3,CWatercress Festival celebrates
OL,4,Csuperfood
OL,6,FWatch: Derek Johnson spent the day in
OL,7,FAlresford
OL,9,FThousands of people have descended on
OL,10,FAlresford to celebrate a salad
OL,11,Fsuperfood.
OL,13,FThe Watercress Festival has been going
OL,14,Ffor more than two decades and has
OL,15,Fgrown into one of Hampshire's biggest
OL,16,Ffood festivals.
OL,18,FIt celebrates the role watercress
OL,19,Fplays in the local economy, history
OL,20,Fand community.
